          <p>Bonobos move to Iowa in the Spring. There is no outdoor exercise yard in place for them at the time they relocate.  There are no climbing structures for them in their cages -- both were promised by the time of relocation. There are no computers in place for them at the time they relocate. It is necessary to press hard to obtain the following basic items necessary for the research, however they are provided
