      <p>Ted insisted that Dr. Sue see a psychiatric counselor regarding my perception of the bonobos capacities. Dr. Sue met with a psychiatric counselor from the Des Moines Counseling Group. After she completed the explanation of events to this professional, he indicated to her that she did not need to continue to seeing him, that she should be seeing a lawyer instead.</p>
      <p><a href="<?php echo get_site_url(); ?>/2022/03/10/material-practices-of-ape-language/">Material Practices of Ape Language</a> is released</p>
